Touchable Video can work seamlessly with social media (Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest), and create value added content.

Rooms is a visually exciting portal to store, organize and safely access all of your favorite sites on the internet. Just like your bedroom, you can decorate your online room to express your style and personality. Fill your room with the sites and apps you visit every day, and discover new ones along the way. Make your room private or share it with friends, family and colleagues. Shop, study, book a vacation, listen to music, watch movies and more, all from the comfort of your Room.

Curing intractable diseases requires innovation. HIV, though now manageable, is still not curable because each new antiretrovirals (ARV) is bounded by the same design principle of interrupting the viral life cycle. HIV eradication requires new therapeutics that seek, identify, and kill cells harboring virus. Aviria has designed an innovative algorithm that combines new therapeutics that we will develop with current ARVs drugs in a precise and novel way that leads to a new outcome – a cure.

Innovation Accelerator builds software tools that improve people's innovation capacity. For just about every reason that humans get stuck while solving problems, we have a technique implemented in software that gets people unstuck. Our first product, Analogy Finder, finds related, adaptable ideas to an engineer's unsolved problem in the U. S. Patent database.

Frictionless Time & Attendance Tracking
EchoTime fills an important need in the world of employee time tracking. In the progression of employee time keeping, we’ve seen the industry move from mechanical machines to electronic and computer-based devices to RFID and NFC enabled systems. Without the high-cost of biometrics or device leasing, we can turn a low-cost Android-device into becoming an efficient and dynamic time-tracking tool full of features not possible with other similar cost systems.

BetterMe is a fun and ingenious new way to wake up in the mornings. The app is for those who will try anything to overcome their groggy morning slumber.
Think of it as a productivity app aimed at using public humiliation as a motivator to help you jump out of the bed in the mornings.
If you snooze, BetterMe will post a message on your Facebook timeline telling all your friends that you were too weak willed to get up in the morning. It's the perfect formula for a better morning.

Sportifik connects sports enthusiasts, and take the hassle out of planning sports games.
We make it easy to organize matches between old friends while also giving users the ability to identify new local players with similar skill levels. By allowing players to organize and track teams, match results, players, and venues, Sportifik also strengthen the local sports community.
Sportifik represents our vision for what an online sports community should look like. We hope you enjoy!

Hot Spot Parking (HSP) is the future of parking. HSP is an autonomous on-street parking management system. Our product is a post that includes a customer read sensor and a vehicle read sensor. From the technology within the posts we offer an automatic payment/enforcement process, a parking availability map, new business advertising mediums, and analytics.

Poll Dingo is a website that will be a large database of opinion polls. Every possible topic and sub-topic you can think of will be filed and questions will be able to be made and anyone can participate in them.They will immediately see results after every click. It will be the unbiased site for political polling as well. This site will be for enterainment but can also be a valuable and credible site to companies who want to know what people want. This is not a survey site, like SurveyMonkey.

Mealmatch is a social fundraising mobile app. Each time a customer checks-in to a restaurant and "matches" their meal using our app, the restaurant donates the cost of another a meal to a feeding project.
Users can see exactly where the matched meal is sent around the world while the restaurant benefits from accessing our charity focused user base, social media sharing, backend tracking account and a loyalty rewards feature.
We currently partner with over 40 restaurants in Arizona.

gottaTxt is a next-gen texting system which lets users add 'geotags' to texts. Recipients can see all geotags on an interactive map. gottaTxt also lets users 'blacklist' numbers, set 'auto-responses' (when phone is dead or user is unavailable), and more.
gottaTxt uses its own servers when sender/recipient are both gottaTxt users, but automatically (and transparently) falls back to SMS when the recipient isn't a user. Nearly all gottaTxt benefits are available, even when friends don't use it.

CineActive is a venue-based interactive social gaming platform delivering gaming and long form interactive content to public and private venues including digital theatres, retail locations and amusement parks. LaunchPress will be available for download from 1st April 2013.

The FieldHouse is a web-based tool designed to help youth sports coaches build successful programs.

Repledge takes money out of the arms race of campaign financing and puts it into more worthy causes. How?
We connect individual contributors who agree to transform their political contributions into charitable donations if a supporter of the opposing political candidate matches the contribution.
This allows political contributors to increase the social utility of their contributions and allows charitable donors to make their voice heard in politics.

Ten million people in the U.S. have brain aneurysms. If the aneurysm is critical, because it has burst, or it may burst, it is treated surgically with either an aneurysm clip or an aneurysm coil. Both of these devices are made of metal and obscure any post-operative MRI or CT imaging of the brain. We have invented a nonmetal aneurysm clip that does not affect imaging, thus enabling accurate, noninvasive evaluation of patients with one or more clipped aneurysms.

The SpotLimit model: "LifeLock for Investors"
1. Retail investors and traders who manage their own accounts through brokers like eTrade register for a monthly fee, and agree to monitoring of their real time trade data
2. In exchange, SpotLimit agrees to reimburse all losses within 12 months of a verified claim up to a set dollar amount.
3. SpotLimit makes money by leveraging member's data investing alongside or hedging against trades through social behavior observations and data analysis.

The Mechaddy is a lever-operated retrofit that replaces the original wheels on a manual wheelchair. It attaches with the same quick-release system found on conventional wheelchairs. Users propel the chair with levers in a chest-press motion. On a forward stroke, it powers the chair forward. The reverse stroke "ratchets" back into position, much like a socket wrench. It can be switched to forward/neutral/reverse, and has a built-in braking system.

Not a HIPAA expert? Never heard of CCD/CCDA, HL7, x12? Don't worry, we'll handle that so you can focus on your core value.
Want to prove your app works? Use our clinical effectiveness analytics.

Plushkies are plush toys with the shape of countries that awake curiosity in kids about the World.
